                  <note>the fact that Finot used italics in his publication shows that he was not sure about his reading of the second <foreign>akṣara</foreign>. The present reading <foreign>re</foreign> is based on the comparison of this occurrence, <foreign>ture vijaya</foreign>, and equivalents found in other inscriptions, namely <foreign>turai vijaya</foreign> and <foreign>turaiy vijaya</foreign> (see, <ref target="C0005.xml">C. 5</ref>, l. 18; <ref target="C0030B2.xml">C. 30 B2</ref>, l. 1; <ref target="C0030B4.xml">C. 30 B4</ref>, l. 2 and <ref target="C0086.xml">C. 86.1</ref>, l. 2. 
